# simple-notes-service

A simple notes service built with Python and FastAPI.

## Features
- CRUD API for notes (in-memory)
- Each note: id (UUID), title (required), content (optional), created_at (ISO timestamp)

## Local Development

### 1. Setup virtual environment

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
```

### 2. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### 3. Run the server

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Access docs at: http://localhost:8000/docs

### 4. Run tests

```bash
pytest -v
```

